Wow, the turnover on these lists lower down is huge - far more than seems practical to manage! But I guess they're a good reference for managing lists higher up.

If you click "Goodreads librarian" under your profile pic, I think you can work out which books have been removed by using the number associated with the edit and adding it to the end of the link - https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/
(and pressing return to load the page)
